HEADWORD: Guernsey lily
<hw>Guern"sey lil"y</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A South
African plant (<spn>Nerine Sarniensis</spn>) with handsome lilylike
flowers, naturalized on the island of Guernsey.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

